      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00001-000-00137"/>lieber,</salute></opener><p><rs ref="#pmb30117" type="work">Sterben</rs>. <hi n="1" rend="underline">Ab<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>olut</hi>
               keine Punkte. Be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>er Novelle als Erzählung, am be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten einfach »von A. S.«</p><p>Bitte hat Ihnen <rs ref="#pmb25488" type="person">Stern</rs> wegen <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00371-1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb34370" subtype="implied">Generalprobe</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00371-1">Zumindest <rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzler</rs> besuchte die <rs type="event" ref="#pmb208690" subtype="implied">Uraufführung</rs> am
                     <date>22. 9. 1894</date> im <rs ref="#pmb118" type="place">Carl-Theater</rs>.</note> was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agen la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en?</p><closer><signed>Hugo.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
